Unsourced material may be challenged and removed. *Find sources:* "Henderson Hill, Singapore" – news **·** newspapers **·** books **·** scholar **·** JSTOR *(July 2018)* *(Learn how and when to remove this message)*Subzone of Bukit Merah Planning Area in Central Region, Singapore **Henderson Hill** ([Chinese](/wiki/Chinese_language): 亨德申山) is a subzone within the planning area of [Bukit Merah](/wiki/Bukit_Merah), Singapore, as defined by the [Urban Redevelopment Authority](/wiki/Urban_Redevelopment_Authority) (URA). Its boundary is composed of Alexandra Road in the north; Lower Delta Road in the east; [Jalan Bukit Merah](/wiki/Jalan_Bukit_Merah,_Singapore) in the south; and the residential precinct along Redhill Close in the east.
